        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:lang="la" resp="#JP">
                <ab>
                    <lb n="1"/><supplied reason="lost">Hic requies</supplied>ci<unclear>t</unclear>
                    <lb n="2"/><supplied reason="lost">in pace fam</supplied>ulus <hi rend="supraline"><expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>e</ex><abbr>i</abbr></expan></hi>
                    <lb n="3"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><supplied reason="lost">a</supplied>bba<supplied reason="lost">s</supplied>
                    <lb n="4"/><supplied reason="lost">qui vixit <expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>nos</ex></expan></supplied> <expan><abbr><unclear><hi rend="supraline">pl</hi></unclear></abbr><ex>us</ex></expan> <supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>inus</ex></expan></supplied><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>
                </ab>
            </div>
            <div type="apparatus">
               <listApp>
                   <app><note>Text of Rizzone 2009, with minor modification line 4 (after photo)</note></app>
                   <app loc="line 1"><note>Isler: CII; </note></app>
                   <app loc="line 2"><note>Isler: [Pa]ulus(?); Isler, Bivona: D(omin)i</note></app>
                   <app loc="line 4"><note>Isler: [---].I[---]; Rizzone [qui vixit an(nos)] pl(us) m(inus)[---]</note></app>
               </listApp>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" xml:lang="en" resp="#JP">
                <p>Here lies in peace the servant of God, Abbot [(name)], who lived [--] years, more or less</p>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" xml:lang="it" resp="#Rizzone2009">
                <p>Qui giace in pace il servo di Dio [---] abate, che visse piu o meno anni [--]</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Rizzone 2009 reconstructs this as a rare record (for Sicily) of a member of a monastic order, in the context of discussing a funerary inscription from Mineo (<ref target="http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic3454">ISic3454</ref>) which appears to record a monk.</p>
            </div>
